snippet.title: [Gameplay] Alien Tequila
snippet.description:
I dedicate this game to all proud Mexicans.
Alien Tequila is nothing more than a "shoot targets" game. It shouldn't exist, but it does, and only in Germany.

Have a taste of what the fuck. .
We also have a Discord server! - https://discord.gg/6JAGtxD
